CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 9, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Flight to Alabama - Mrs. Daisy Oliver, left, Mrs. Darline Dumas, center, and Mrs. Amanda Nichols flew to Birmingham, Ala. last week via Capitol Air Lines to visit Mrs. Oliver's sister, Mrs. Lulu Hughes, who is seriously ill. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Daisy Oliver, Darline Dumas, and Amanda Nichols wearing suits and posed between parted dark curtains in Harris Studio
